<html>
  <head>
    <title>Strada: Help</title>
    <%= partial 'public/partials/_head.html.erb' %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p class='icon'>
      <a href='/'><img src='img/icon.png'></a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <h1>Strada: Help</h1>
    </p>
    <p>
      This bot is powered by Strava and posts your Strava activities to Discord.
      It is not made by, nor is officially affiliated with <a target="_blank" href="https://www.strava.com">Strava</a>.
    </p>
    <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <p>
      <img src="img/help.png">
    </p>
    <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <p>
      Use <b>/strada connect</b> to connect your Strava account and <b>/strada disconnect</b> to disconnect. Follow the prompts. Notifications will be sent to the channel where you connected.
    </p>
    <p>
      Try <b>/strada leaderboard</b> to see a distance leaderboard, or <b>/strada stats</b> to see aggregate stats in the current channel for the past 30 days.
      Try <b>/strada leaderboard distance</b>, <b>/strada leaderboard time</b> or <b>/strada leaderboard count</b>.
      Leaderboard supports longer ranges which may require adjusting <b>retention</b>.
      Try <b>/strada leaderboard last week</b>, or <b>/strada leaderboard elapsed time last month</b>.
      Leaderboard also understands <b>since 2024</b> or <b>between January and March</b>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Stop syncing activities with <b>/strada set sync false</b> and resume with <b>/strada set sync true</b> (default).
      Publish private (only you) activities with <b>/strada set private true</b> or hide them with <b>/strada set private false</b> (default).
      Publish followers only activities with <b>/strada set followers true</b> (default) or hide them with <b>/strada set followers false</b>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Strada retains activities for 30 days. Discord server admins can change this with <b>/strada set retention 60 days</b> or <b>/strada set retention 3 months</b> to change this.
      Change <b>units</b> with <b>/strada set units imperial</b> (miles, feet, yards, and degrees Fahrenheit, default), <b>/strada set units metric</b> (kilometers, meters, and degrees Celsius), or <b>/strada set units both</b> to display both values.
      Change displayed fields with <b>/strada set fields</b>, eg. <b>/strada set fields default</b>, <b>/strada set fields all</b> or <b>/strada set fields none</b>.
      Available fields are <%= ActivityFields.values.and { |v| '<b>' + v + '</b>' } %>.
      Turn maps off with <b>/strada set maps off</b>, display thumbnails with <b>/strada set maps thumb</b> and full maps with <b>/strada set maps full</b> (default).
      Disconnect users with <b>/strada disconnect @mention</b>.
    </p>
    <%= partial 'public/partials/_footer.html.erb' %>
  </body>
</html>

